Add a sentence to JSON Format, section 19.2 (and the corresponding section on Multipart Batch in Protocol):
{quote}If the {{Location}} header in the response contains a relative URL, clients MUST be able to resolve it relative to the request's URL even if that contains such a reference.
{quote}
